                     "display_title": "Republic Attack Gunship™",
                     "description": "Take the battle to the Separatists with this heavily armed troop transporter, as seen in Star Wars: The Clone Wars. Features opening crew bay doors, flick missiles, and separate speeder bike. Includes seven minifigures: 4 clone troopers, Obi-Wan Kenobi, and two new minifigures, Plo Koon and Asajj Ventress, a Sith Lord equipped with a new double lightsaber.",
